<div id="post-431059" class="blog-post position-8 even-post"><div class="even-post-inner blog-post-inner"><h1 class="title"><a href="http://softwarelivre.org/libreoffice/blog/hackfest-date">Hackfest date</a></h1><span class="publishing-info"><span class="date">13 de Maio de 2012, 0:00</span><span class="author">, por Software Livre Brasil</span><span class="comments"> - <a href="/libreoffice/blog/hackfest-date#comments_list"><span class='comment-count hide'>0</span><span class='comment-count-write-out'>sem comentários ainda</span></a></span></span><p>This is another reminder to cast your vote for the Hackfest, since we would like to fix and announce the date soon.</p>
<p>The available options are listed in this poll: <a href="http://www.doodle.com/sz6eehwtn57f765a">http://www.doodle.com/sz6eehwtn57f765a</a></p>
